---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <nav class="fixed w-full top-0 z-50 glass-panel border-b border-t-0 border-x-0">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group -ml-2" aria-label="NextReach Studio - Home">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="NextReach Studio" width="32" height="32" class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110" />
          <span class="text-white text-sm tracking-[0.08em] font-medium hidden sm:inline">NextReach Studio</span>
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="mailto:hello@nextreachstudio.com" class="text-zinc-500 text-xs hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors duration-300 hidden sm:block">hello@nextreachstudio.com</a>
          <button onclick="window.dispatchEvent(new Event('open-chat-widget'))" class="text-sm font-bold bg-amber-400 text-black px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full tracking-[0.08em] uppercase hover:bg-amber-300 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_28px_rgba(251,191,36,0.25)] min-h-[44px] flex items-center cursor-pointer">Free Demo</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="pt-32 px-6 sm:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-500 mb-4">About</p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-semibold text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white tracking-[-0.01em] mb-6 leading-[1.2]">
          Built by operators who hate missing calls
        </h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-[1.7] text-lg">
          We&rsquo;re a small team that builds AI tools for independent service businesses. We started with pet grooming because that&rsquo;s what we know.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 mb-40 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Every day, thousands of calls go unanswered at pet grooming salons across the country. Clients ring, no one picks up, and they book somewhere else. That&rsquo;s thousands in lost revenue every month.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          We built NextReach Studio to fix that. An AI receptionist that answers 24/7, knows your prices and services, and books appointments while you focus on grooming.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          We believe in simple, honest tools that solve real problems. No AI hype. No complicated setup. Just a receptionist that works, built by people who understand the business.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-white/[0.06] pt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">
            Questions? <a href="mailto:hello@nextreachstudio.com" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors">hello@nextreachstudio.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
